      "DialogueText_10_10D44AC44144EC85326507BD9E2D1C2A": "NSLOCTEXT(\"\", \"151950ED4C733B319E0BE8A6C3ABFBA4\", \"We have it. Before we do anything with it though, tell me what it is. And who you are. And why you want it badly enough to risk ARC detecting your comms.\")",
